Class JkTestSuiteResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jerkar.api.java.junit.JkTestSuiteResult
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class JkTestSuiteResult
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    A result of a test suite execution. It contains both overall information about suite execution and details about each test case execution.
